This paper proposes a novel framework that integrates recommender systems and dialog generation systems. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
